OL,3,CSalmon fishing festival returns to
OL,4,CScottish Borders
OL,6,FA festival aiming to celebrate salmon
OL,7,Ffishing in the River Tweed is
OL,8,Freturning this weekend.
OL,10,FThe second Tweed Salmon Festival is
OL,11,Fbeing held on Saturday and Sunday near
OL,12,FKelso in the Scottish Borders.
OL,14,FLocal anglers and fly-casters have
OL,15,Forganised the event, which last year
OL,16,Fattracted nearly 1,000 people.
OL,18,FThis year the organisers promise the
OL,19,Fevent will be bigger than ever,
OL,20,Fincluding fishing demonstrations and
OL,21,Fintroductions to trying the sport out.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
