PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1777381871
OL,3,CSalmon fishing festival returns to
OL,4,CScottish Borders
OL,6,FLast year just under 100 people said
OL,7,Fthey had caught their first ever fish
OL,8,Fat the event.
OL,10,FEoin Fairgrieve is the main organiser.
OL,11,FHe told ITV Border: "We're looking at
OL,12,Fa very positive path into fly-fishing,
OL,13,Fin an environment where people can get
OL,14,Fqualified fly-casting instruction.
OL,16,F"It's a very positive, inclusive
OL,17,Fenvironment, and we want to see more
OL,18,Fnext generation anglers on the water.
OL,20,F"We want people to come together -
OL,21,Fit's a community event."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
