OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1777381871
OL,3,CSalmon fishing festival returns to
OL,4,CScottish Borders
OL,6,FThe free festival will this year host
OL,7,FWild Fish, Wild Places, a Scandinavian
OL,8,Fdocumentary series which will feature
OL,9,Fthe event and take a look at fishing
OL,10,Fon the Tweed.
OL,12,FIn addition, the 'Riverside Journal'
OL,13,Fwill be launched, with articles
OL,14,Flooking at the history of salmon
OL,15,Ffishing in the Borders.
OL,17,FThe festival organisers would also
OL,18,Flike to see more women give the sport
OL,19,Fa go. Sarah Ronholt will lead
OL,20,Fsessions, and she founded the 'Fish
OL,21,Fand Chicks' group.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
