OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1777381871
OL,3,CSalmon fishing festival returns to
OL,4,CScottish Borders
OL,6,FSarah said: "I just think that it's
OL,7,Fsuper important to have more people
OL,8,Fengaged in fly-fishing.
OL,10,F"This is a place where you can find a
OL,11,Fmuch more approachable way (into the
OL,12,Fsport).
OL,14,F"Fly-fishing is an amazing way to
OL,15,Fspend time outside, and to connect
OL,16,Fwith other people. The places it takes
OL,17,Fyou, these are the key reasons why I
OL,18,Flove it so much."
